397
00:26:09,599 --> 00:26:10,640
The living can talk,

398
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:11,519
but they also lie.

399
00:26:11,799 --> 00:26:13,960
The dead can't even say a word.

400
00:26:16,839 --> 00:26:19,119
My scalpel can make them talk.

401
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:20,839
Awesome.

402
00:26:21,240 --> 00:26:21,839
Qi Xia?

403
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:24,559
Qi Xia?

404
00:26:30,480 --> 00:26:31,359
