432
00:27:57,920 --> 00:27:58,920
Indeed.

433
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:00,359
And effective too.

434
00:28:00,720 --> 00:28:02,799
By finding the injector,

435
00:28:03,039 --> 00:28:05,880
the police can use it
to convict Song En.

436
00:28:12,079 --> 00:28:13,279
I've been to Lai La's house.

437
00:28:13,799 --> 00:28:16,200
